<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="go-so-far-as-far-as-to-do-sth">go so far / as far as to do sth</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>[口语] 竟然做某事；甚至做某事：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She goes so far as to declare that a Chinese word can never give you the exact meaning of a word in English!
她甚至说，汉语词绝对不能表达英语词的确切含义。</p><footer>2010 辽宁改</footer></div></div>